Catherine Rouvel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catherine_Rouvel 0 Catherine Rouvel (born Catherine Vitale; 31 August 1939 in Marseille) is an acclaimed French actress. Her career spans from 1959 in television to 2004. She starred in Jean Renoir's Le Déjeuner sur l'herbe, Marcel Carné's Les Assassins de l'ordre and in the 1976 Jean Jacques Annaud film Black and White in Color.
